    public class ZZI
extends ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractSegment
    The ZZI segment is intended to be used for information that support distributed tracing across system boundaries using Zipkin. Also see http://zipkin.io/pages/instrumenting.html for details
    Author:
    Christian Ohr
